"4119","Ambulance Services","Emergency transportation services with trained personnel that may\\nor may not provide emergency medical treatment en route to a\\nhospital or medical provider.","Transportation","CCR3 CR03 OTH1 OTH2 OTH3 OTH4 OTH5 OTH6 OT11 OT12 OT13 OT14 OT15 OT16 OT21 OT22 OT25 OT32","BEL1 BR07 BR10 CHLH CHNA COLJ JA02 OTH8 OT33 OT34 OT36 OT39 OT40 OT41 TT01-TTO UR06"
"4121","Limousines and Taxicabs","Passenger automobile transportation services that do not operate\\non a regular schedule or an established route.","Transportation","CCR1 CNV2 CR04 OTH1 OTH2 OTH3 OTH4 OTH5 OTH6 OT11 OT12 OT13 OT14 OT15 OT16 OT21 OT22 OT25 OT32 ST01","ARG2 AUS4 BEL1 BR03 BR08 CAN4 CHLB CHLL CHN8 CHN9 CHNA COLG EM03 JA02 JPN3 OTH8 OT33 OT34 OT36 QPS1 OT39 OT40 OT41 PA02 SPN3 TR01-TTO UR06"
"4131","Bus Lines","Passenger bus transportation services that operate on a regular\\nschedule over predetermined routes.\\nFor charter and tour bus operators, use MCC 4722.","Transportation","CCR1 CR04 GW01 OTH1 OTH2 OTH3 OTH4 OTH5 OTH6 OT11 OT12 OT13 OT14 OT15 OT16 OT21 OT22 OT25 OT32 ST01","AUS3 AUS4 BEL1 BR03 BR08 CHLE CHLL CHN8 CHN9 CHNA COLE JA02 JPN3 OTH8 OT33 OT34 OT36 PR06 QPS1 OT39 OT40 OT41 SPN3 TT01-TTO UR06"
"4214","Motor Freight Carriers, Trucking: Local/Long Distance, Moving and Storage","Local or long distance trucking services that may or may not also\\nprovide storage services.\\nFor household goods warehousing and storage without trucking\\nservices, use MCC 4225.\\nFor couriers of parcels, goods, and packages, use MCC 4215.","Transportation","CCR3 CF01 CR03 OTH1 OTH2 OTH3 OTH4 OTH5 OTH6 OT11 OT12 OT13 OT14 OT15 OT16 OT21 OT22 OT25 OT32","BR07 BR10 CHLG CHNA COLE JA02 JPNG OTH8 OT33 OT34 OT39 OT40 OT41 SPN3 UR06"
"4215","Courier Services: Air and Ground, Freight Forwarders","Merchants that deliver individually addressed letters, parcels and\\npackages (excluding Postal Services: Government Only: MCC 9402).\\nFor merchants that provide trucking delivery of freight, use MCC\\n4214.","Transportation","undefined","BEL1 BR03 BR08 CHLG CHLM CHNA COLE IDN2 JA02 OTH8 OT33 OT34 OT36 OT39 OT40 OT41 TT01-TTO UR06"
"4225","Public Warehousing; Farm Products, Refrigerated Goods, Household Goods","Providers of storage and warehousing for farm products,\\nrefrigerated storage for perishable products, and storage for\\nhousehold goods and furniture.\\nFor merchants that provide local storage and trucking services, use\\nMCC 4214.","Transportation","CCR3 CR03 OTH1 OTH2 OTH3 OTH4 OTH5 OTH6 OT11 OT12 OT13 OT14 OT15 OT16 OT21 OT22 OT25 OT32","BEL1 BR07 BR10 CHLG CHNA COLN JA02 JPNG OTH8 OT33 OT34 OT36 OT39 OT40 OT41 TT01-TTO UR06"
